Name: Awesome Obstacle Challenge
About the game: Show off your mad Awesome Obstacle Challenge skills in a VR-ONLY race to the finish. Run, climb, and leap your way through dozens of obstacle courses to see if you can finish on top of the global charts. Climb walls, nets, and ropes. Traverse high canyons. Tiptoe across balance beams. True champions will encounter lasers, fires and more ! Prove yourself and take the Awesome Obstacle Challenge!
